%p#notice= notice

%p
  %b= @activity.name

Mentors:
- @activity.interests.where(wants_to_mentor: true).each do |interest, user = interest.user|
  %br
  = link_to user.name, interest_path(interest.id)
  = user.email

%br
Mentees:
- @activity.interests.where(wants_to_be_mentored: true).each do |interest, user = interest.user|
  %br
  = link_to user.name, interest_path(interest.id)
  = user.email

%br
All interested:
- @activity.interests.each do |interest, user = interest.user|
  %br
  = link_to user.name, interest_path(interest.id)
  = user.email